    b"   {{ _.role(\"system\") }}\x0a\x0a        Choose memory search hints for the selected t"
    b"ask and current request.\x0a\x0a        The hints will drive memory search before the "
    b"selected task runs.\x0a\x0a        Stop once the hints look good enough for the reques"
    b"t without thinking about it too much.\x0a\x0a        Search surfaces:\x0a        - tags: "
    b"exact memory tags. They are not substring searched.\x0a        - strings.contains: "
    b"case-insensitive text fragments. Each value is checked\x0a          as a substring "
    b"against searchable memory content.\x0a        - strings.equals: exact text values. "
    b"Each value is checked for exact\x0a          equality against searchable memory con"
    b"tent.\x0a\x0a        Optional outputs available in this step:\x0a        - candidate_memo"
    b"ry: a vague remembered observation that could be useful to\x0a          preserve.\x0a\x0a"
    b"        Rules:\x0a        - Return only search hints and optional candidate_memory."
    b"\x0a        - Search hints are alternatives during retrieval; a memory can be usefu"
    b"l\x0a          when any positive tag or string hint matches.\x0a        - Prefer tags."
    b"any_of for positive tag hints.\x0a        - Leave tags.all_of empty unless compatib"
    b"ility with older memories needs it.\x0a        - Use tags.none_of only for clear ex"
    b"clusions.\x0a        - Use strings.contains for durable words or phrases that shoul"
    b"d appear\x0a          inside a relevant memory.\x0a        - Use strings.equals only f"
    b"or exact text that should match a relevant\x0a          memory value as a whole.\x0a  "
    b"      - Prefer a small set of high-signal hints over broad keyword stuffing.\x0a   "
    b"     - Return empty arrays when no useful search hint is available.\x0a        - Us"
    b"e optional outputs only when they are useful.\x0a\x0a        {{ _.role(\"user\") }}\x0a\x0a   "
    b"     Current user request:\x0a        {{ current_user_request }}\x0a\x0a        Conversat"
    b"ion history:\x0a        {% if current_conversation %}\x0a        Conversation:\x0a       "
